Compiling Instructions
======================

The compilation of USUT is very straight forward, just 
follow this easy steps:

1- Install libusb*.
2- Go to the source directory of the test, and execute:
	#make
3- In case of getting "error while loading shared 
libraries" you need to execute:
	#sudo ldconfig


* It was developed with libusb-1.0.6 version
